{"tid":815629,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上周新蒲崗離家失蹤　男子伏屍墳場山澗","createTime":"2018-09-12T07:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T07:51:53.000Z","uid":150685,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1dee90557f92a13675530169752abe4b08f2f528","tid":815629,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T07:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180912/photo/bkn-20180912075421971-0912_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180912131358\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180912%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180912075421971-0912_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180912131358&h=af6fcc86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晨(12日)6時58分，有工人在毓華街100號救世軍卜維廉中學對開鑽石山墳場近山澗位置，發現一名年約60歲男子倒斃，並傳出陣陣惡臭，大驚報警求助。警員及救護員趕至，證實男子已經死去一段時間，警方封鎖現場，經調查後證實死者為一名失蹤男子。<br />\n<br />\n早上11時許，死者兩名女兒到場助查，確認死者為失蹤64歲男子駱堯毓。駱於上周四（6日）上午離開於新蒲崗景福街的住所後便告失蹤，其家人同日向警方報案。駱身高約1.65米，體重約54公斤，瘦身材，尖面型，黃皮膚及蓄短直黑髮。他最後露面時身穿灰色短袖上衣、藍色牛仔褲、藍色拖鞋及攜有一個灰色及黑色環保袋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180912/bkn-20180912075421971-0912_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180912%2Fbkn-20180912075421971-0912_00822_001.html&d=JFdDtS5NL7a8ORdY22CG7ZzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=fe7b49f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180912/bkn-20180912075421971-0912_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 墳場"},{"pid":"45ad5309441498f9922d5a316e552876dee7e977","tid":815629,"uid":47147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T07:49:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f781cbbb44da8c743a7b3b5a5750feb58ec3f65f","tid":815629,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T07:51:53.000Z","msg":"搵替身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}